Emacs 31 adds a Theme (as in collection of user options, not a color scheme) for new users.  You can enable it by loading the `newcomers-presets' theme, or on the startup screen.  

The options this theme enables might change over time, depending on new features being added or deprecated by others.

You can fine the current definition of the theme, including the options it enabled here: https://cgit.git.savannah.gnu.org/cgit/emacs.git/tree/etc/themes/newcomers-presets-theme.el.
